@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Role of a router

[LAN A] as lana
[Router] as r
[LAN B] as lanb

lana --> r : IP packets
r --> lanb : IP packets

note right of r
  Router:
  - connects networks
  - decides next hop / interface
  - uses the routing table
  - can filter / modify (NAT, ACL)
end note
@enduml
